skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cat sounds
des:
This skill plays a variety of cat sounds! From the cat's meow to the kittens mew! All of the purr-fect sounds for the cat connoisseur and lover of meow-sic!

The sounds are around 10 to 30 seconds each with many different sounds and cat puns for your listening pleasure. After each sound is played, you can hear another by answering, "yes," or you can just meow!

To start the fun, simply say, "Alexa open cat sounds!"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
